00:32:08.055 --> 00:32:10.150
RETO MEIER: Oh, of course.

00:32:10.150 --> 00:32:13.930
IAN NI-LEWIS: So with TripIt,
you're going to have--

00:32:13.930 --> 00:32:16.660
