00:32:25.500 --> 00:32:27.660
IAN NI-LEWIS: The idea with
TripIt is that it's all of

00:32:27.660 --> 00:32:29.970
your travel information
in one place.

00:32:29.970 --> 00:32:34.110
And it's going to show you the
most relevant thing first and

00:32:34.110 --> 00:32:36.710
try and remove all the
irrelevant nonsense.

00:32:36.710 --> 00:32:39.980
So it needs to know what time
