00:32:39.980 --> 00:32:41.270
where you are.

00:32:41.270 --> 00:32:46.220
So in this particular case,
for instance, knowing that

00:32:46.220 --> 00:32:50.290
we're going from Melbourne to
Perth is only important if we

00:32:50.290 --> 00:32:51.740
