00:32:51.740 --> 00:32:52.590
RETO MEIER: Yeah.

00:32:52.590 --> 00:32:54.160
IAN NI-LEWIS: And you
could find that in

00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:55.930
two different ways.

00:32:55.930 --> 00:32:59.400
You could find that out either
through location or by time.

00:32:59.400 --> 00:33:01.875
But probably location is a
little safer because the

00:33:01.875 --> 00:33:03.380
