RETO MEIER: Exactly.

00:34:23.100 --> 00:34:26.770
So let's have a look at some of
the things which you should

00:34:26.770 --> 00:34:29.280
be able to do and
do really well.

00:34:29.280 --> 00:34:30.699
So knowing where we
are is important.

00:34:30.699 --> 00:34:35.320
But it's much more important
that I get my itinerary

00:34:35.320 --> 00:34:37.179
changes as quickly
as possible.

00:34:37.179 --> 00:34:38.280
And as I mentioned--

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:41.140
let me see if I can drop
