00:34:41.140 --> 00:34:42.600
It's neater.

00:34:42.600 --> 00:34:44.100
Ah, that looks a bit weird.

00:34:44.100 --> 00:34:48.380
Nonetheless, but this does
set up a conflict.

00:34:48.380 --> 00:34:53.340
And like we said, it's that
idea of we want things to

00:34:53.340 --> 00:34:54.909
happen straightaway, but we
don't want to have to do these

00:34:54.909 --> 00:34:56.440
manual updates.

00:34:56.440 --> 00:34:59.990
And so what that does
is that we--

00:34:59.990 --> 00:35:01.400
IAN NI-LEWIS: I love these
