not see it all and see a

00:40:57.070 --> 00:40:58.760
loading bar or a progress
bar instead.

00:40:58.760 --> 00:41:00.650
RETO MEIER: Absolutely.

00:41:00.650 --> 00:41:03.940
So it's probably also worth
mentioning that network state

00:41:03.940 --> 00:41:07.690
and the type of network that
you're connected to you can

00:41:07.690 --> 00:41:10.710
also be really important in
determining the frequency of

00:41:10.710 --> 00:41:12.760
your data transfers and the
aggressiveness of your

00:41:12.760 --> 00:41:13.340
pre-fetching.

00:41:13.340 --> 00:41:15.220
So you can actually monitor
all of that.

00:41:15.220 --> 00:41:17.560
