00:41:28.420 --> 00:41:30.810
So we're going to increase it
when we're on Wi-Fi or on 4G,

00:41:30.810 --> 00:41:33.870
or we're going to drop it down
when we're on slower networks.

00:41:33.870 --> 00:41:35.970
And so again, what we're doing
here is trying to find a

00:41:35.970 --> 00:41:40.260
better balance between battery
drain and latency reduction.

